data.description: There is real comfort in this nicely-kept, light and airy plan creekfront(Trout Stocked) multi-level offering plentiful space on 0.65 acres. Here is a lovely multiple level home that varies the look of the conventional home. 3 bedrooms, 3 baths. You will enjoy the luxury of living close to recreation/shops. Visitors find an instant welcome with the circular drive. Ingenious design means meal magic from this custom kitchen with kitchen appliances included. Everything is tidy and tucked away when you have the ample storage space. Catch your breath and a breeze on your own 3-season porch. Nothing could add more allure to a property than the proximity of the native landscape. Also deserving of attention are these included features: open & airy design, 2-story great room, loft and fireplace. Beamed, cathedral ceilings, wood flooring, muted decor colors, main-level master bedroom, loft style bedroom, underground utilities, finished walk-out basement, metal roof, multi-level large view deck, fishing, mature trees, city utilities and water, all-weather access. It is so easy-to-love, so easy to live in! Prompt possession.
